# Planning and subagent accountability

When drafting or updating an implementation plan, include **Subagent reports and follow-ups** when **decky-debugger** (or another specialist) applies or was used. Summarize findings and cite `.cursor/agents/SUBAGENT_REPORTS.md` (Report log).

Before closing risky work (RPC, logging, permissions, focus/layout), state triage vs deferred follow-up.
